<table width="auto"  border="0" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tr><td colspan=3>House Bill/Resolution NO. <b>PS00063</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>FULL TITLE : BAGUIO, LA TRINIDAD, IITOGON, SUBLAY, TUBA, TUBLAY DEVELOPMENT AUTHORITY (BLISTTDA)</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SHORT TITLE : Housing Requirement</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>ABSTRACT : ... Rep. Go stressed the need to rehabilitate and ensure the progress of Baguio City and its five adjacent municipalities ... Benguet, La Trinidad, 
Itogon, Sablan, Tuba and Tublay (BLISTT) through 
the creation of a BLISTT Development Authority 
(BLISTTDA)...; explained how a once-clean, cosmopolitan, and uncrowded city had become a jungle of congestion, waste, traffic, informal settlements, and an increasing population due to rapid urbanization without a wellprepared development plan...; said that  he had filed House Bill No. 1554 seeking the creation of the BLISTTDA ...; relayed to the Body the salient and pertinent
provisions of House Bill No. 1554,... stated that the creation of the BLISTTDA offers a road map to bring back the glory days of the said areas adjacent to Baguio City and to achieve a sustainable social and economic growth for the interest and benefit of the people of Baguio City... (House Journal No.20,pp.5-6)  </td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>PRINCIPAL AUTHOR/S : <b>GO, MARK O.</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>DATE FILED : 2016-09-07</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>SIGNIFICANCE: NATIONAL</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>NATURE : Speech-Privilege Hour</td></tr><tr><td colspan=3><b>ACTIONS TAKEN BY THE COMMITTEE ON RULES</b></td></tr><tr><td colspan=3>REFERRAL TO THE COMMITTEE ON GOVERNMENT ENTERPRISES AND PRIVATIZATION ON 2016-09-14</td></tr></table>